        <p><a href="http://www.enisa.europa.eu/../activities/Resilience-and-CIIP/files/resilience-video-2010/" class="internal-link" title="Resilience Video 2010"><img src="http://www.enisa.europa.eu/activities/Resilience-and-CIIP/files/Resilience-Video-2010.jpg/image_thumb" title="Resilience Video 2010" height="66" width="128" alt="Resilience Video 2010" class="image-inline" /></a></p>
<p> </p>
<p><a href="http://www.enisa.europa.eu/../activities/identity-and-trust/library/videos/what-is-resilience-and-how-enisa-is-approaching-it" class="internal-link" title="What is resilience and how ENISA is approaching it"><img src="http://www.enisa.europa.eu/activities/Resilience-and-CIIP/files/enisa_resilience_small.jpg" title="Resilience video" height="66" width="128" alt="Resilience video" class="image-inline" /></a></p>
        
